.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: blue, green, red, white, yellow
There are 5 different nationalities: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
The people have 5 different jobs:  security-guard, project-manager, lawyer, fisherman, writer
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
The people have 5 different hobbies: gardening, board-games, chess, puzzles, skydiving
1. the british is the person who likes red
2. the swedish is the person who's hobby is chess
3. the danish is the fisherman
4. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes white
5. the person who likes green is the project-manager
6. the pall-mall-smoker is the person who's hobby is board-games
7. the person who likes yellow is the dunhill-smoker
8. the lawyer is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening
11. the person who's hobby is skydivings is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker
12. the bluemaster-smoker is the security-guard
13. the german is the prince-smoker
14. the norwegian is on the left or right of the person who likes blue
15. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the writer

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    yellow	|     blue	|      red	|     green	|     white	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    danish	|    british	|    german	|    swedish	|
| Hobby		|     gardening	|    skydiving	|     board-games	|     puzzles	|      chess	|
| Job	|    writer	|     fisherman	|     lawyer	|    project-manager	|      security-guard	|
| Cigar		|   dunhill	|    blend	|  pall-mall	|    prince	|   bluemaster	|
